## 3. Code "Release Quality" Checklist
*   [ ] **Remove Absolute Paths**: Ensure all file paths in [app.py](file:///Users/jagdishs/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/fabric-estimator/app.py) are relative.
*   [ ] **Secret Management**: Ensure no private keys or personal data are in the code.
*   [ ] **Performance**: The V3.0 Pixel Engine is CPU intensive. On a free server like Streamlit Cloud, it might be slow. Consider adding a "Demo Mode" with lower defaults.
*   [ ] **Comments**: Add docstrings to functions like [PixelPacker](file:///Users/jagdishs/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/fabric-estimator/app.py#229-354) to explain the logic to contributors.

